---
title: Kasporio
---

Kasporio better known as Kasporio the Cunning, is the second in command of the mercenary company the Second Sons.

Kasporio is slim and elegant, with a pointed beard. He wields a slender bravos blade with a jeweled hilt. He wears a slashed pink doublet. Tyrion considers him not-so-cunning and a jackanapes. 


